The House of Sand;;79;;79;;R;;After their patriarch (Ruy Guerra) dies in an accident, a pregnant woman (Fernanda Torres) and her mother (Fernanda Montenegro) must fend for themselves in a harsh desert in northern Brazil. Befriended by a local man (Luiz Melodia), they establish a modest home, and the younger one, Aurea, dreams of escape, but the older one, Dona Maria, learns to accept her fate.;;Drama;;Andrucha Waddington;;2006;;Fernanda Montenegro,Fernanda Torres,Ruy Guerra,Seu Jorge,Luiz Melodia,Enrique Díaz,Stênio Garcia,Emiliano Queiroz,Camilla Facundes,João Acaiabe,Haroldo Costa,Jorge Mautner,Nélson Jacobina,Jefferson de Almeida Barbosa,Wadson Martins Costa;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_sand